Package com.hexaware.entity

Class Payroll

java.lang.Object
com.hexaware.entity.Payroll
public class Payroll extends Object
The 'Payroll' class represents the payroll information of the employee. It has various attributes such as payrollId, employeeId, payPeriodStartDate, payPeriodEndDate, basicSalary, overtimePay, deductions and netsalary. This class is used to create, access and retrieve the payroll details.
